      <title>不丹自由派托盖伊在第四次自由投票后成为总理</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/bhutans-liberal-tobgay-becomes-prime-minister-after-fourth-free-vote-2024-01-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[不丹自由派政治家、人民民主党（PDP）领导人策林·托盖（Tshering Tobgay）在本月早些时候的选举后于周日正式开始他的第二个总理任期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/bhutans-liberal-tobgay-becomes-prime-minister-after-fourth-free-vote-2024-01-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 13:34:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国允许菲律宾向争议岛礁派遣部队</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-allows-philippines-supply-troops-disputed-reef-2024-01-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国海警表示，已做出“临时特别安排”，允许菲律宾通过一艘停泊在争议礁石上的二战时期船只向部队运送物资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-allows-philippines-supply-troops-disputed-reef-2024-01-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 13:08:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>教皇呼吁结束战争并敦促尊重平民</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/pope-calls-an-end-wars-urges-respect-civilians-2024-01-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[教皇方济各周日敦促尊重冲突地区的平民，并表示人们厌倦了战争，他称战争是“人民的灾难和人类的失败”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/pope-calls-an-end-wars-urges-respect-civilians-2024-01-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 12:43:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚新南威尔士州总理谴责新纳粹集会</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australias-new-south-wales-state-premier-condemns-neo-nazi-rally-2024-01-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚新南威尔士州州长周日谴责该州首府悉尼的新纳粹集会“令人震惊”，此前一天，总理安东尼·阿尔巴内斯表示该国新纳粹主义正在抬头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australias-new-south-wales-state-premier-condemns-neo-nazi-rally-2024-01-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 05:38:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国与泰国签署互免签证协议</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-china-sign-mutual-visa-waiver-agreements-2024-01-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国和中国周日同意免除对方国民的签证要求，以促进受新冠肺炎 (COVID-19) 影响的两国之间的旅行和旅游业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-china-sign-mutual-visa-waiver-agreements-2024-01-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 05:26:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>古特雷斯：联合国将惩罚参与“恐怖”的工作人员</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/guterres-un-punish-staffers-involved-terror-urges-unrwa-funding-2024-01-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一些难民机构工作人员被指控参与 10 月 7 日哈马斯对以色列的袭击后，联合国秘书长安东尼奥·古特雷斯周日誓言要追究“任何参与恐怖行为的联合国雇员”的责任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/guterres-un-punish-staffers-involved-terror-urges-unrwa-funding-2024-01-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 05:03:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜在东海岸发射巡航导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-fired-multiple-cruise-missiles-south-korea-military-2024-01-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国参谋长联席会议（JCS）表示，朝鲜周日在东海岸发射了多枚巡航导弹，这是不到一周内第二次发射此类导弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-fired-multiple-cruise-missiles-south-korea-military-2024-01-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 02:26:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>更多国家暂停向联合国巴勒斯坦机构提供资金</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/britain-italy-finland-pause-funding-un-refugee-agency-gaza-2024-01-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国、意大利、荷兰和芬兰因指控联合国巴勒斯坦难民机构的部分工作人员参与了 10 月 7 日哈马斯对以色列的袭击而暂停了资助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/britain-italy-finland-pause-funding-un-refugee-agency-gaza-2024-01-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 15:11:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国和中国高级官员在曼谷讨论台湾和伊朗问题</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-wang-says-taiwan-issue-biggest-threat-sino-us-ties-2024-01-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在总统乔·拜登和中国领导人习近平预计春季通话之前，中国和美国高级官员在曼谷举行坦诚会谈，旨在缓解超级大国之间在台湾和其他问题上的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-wang-says-taiwan-issue-biggest-threat-sino-us-ties-2024-01-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 15:06:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国将宣布对先进芯片提供数十亿美元的补贴 - 华尔街日报</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-announce-billions-subsidies-advanced-chips-wsj-2024-01-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《华尔街日报》周六报道，总统乔·拜登的政府预计将在未来几周内向英特尔和台积电等顶级半导体公司提供数十亿美元的补贴，以帮助在美国建设新工厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-announce-billions-subsidies-advanced-chips-wsj-2024-01-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 10:56:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
